</text><text x=\"50\" y=\"194\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"1\" opacity=\"1\">DEPTH ANSWER</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"212\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Based on 3 decision records and 8 messages</text><line x1=\"34\" y1=\"222\" x2=\"356\" y2=\"222\" stroke=\"#1E2035\" stroke-width=\"1\" opacity=\"1\"/><text x=\"34\" y=\"234\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#9EA3C0\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Your team chose Clerk over Auth0 primarily for</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"248\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#9EA3C0\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">three reasons captured in the Apr 8 decision:</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"276\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">1. Clerk's built-in MFA meets your SOC 2 Type II</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"290\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">   requirements without additional code.</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"304\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">2. Auth0 pricing would increase ~3× at your scale.</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"318\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">3. Clerk's SDK has native Next.js integration,</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"332\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">   reducing migration complexity.</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"346\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Sources cited:</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"358\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">↗ Auth migration decision (Apr 8)</text><text x=\"34\" y=\"370\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">↗ #backend-team messages (12)</text><text x=\"200\" y=\"358\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">↗ Vendor evaluation doc</text><text x=\"20\" y=\"378\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"1.5\" opacity=\"1\">FOLLOW-UP QUESTIONS</text><rect x=\"20\" y=\"394\" width=\"350\" height=\"44\" fill=\"#161828\" rx=\"10\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#818CF822\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"36\" y=\"420\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">What's the rollback plan if Clerk fails?</text><text x=\"356\" y=\"420\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">→</text><rect x=\"20\" y=\"446\" width=\"350\" height=\"44\" fill=\"#161828\" rx=\"10\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#818CF822\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"36\" y=\"472\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">How long is the migration expected to take?</text><text x=\"356\" y=\"472\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">→</text><rect x=\"20\" y=\"498\" width=\"350\" height=\"44\" fill=\"#161828\" rx=\"10\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#818CF822\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"36\" y=\"524\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#E0E2F4\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Which engineers are leading this?</text><text x=\"356\" y=\"524\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"end\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">→</text><text x=\"20\" y=\"554\" font-size=\"10\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"700\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"1.5\" opacity=\"1\">RECENT QUERIES</text><rect x=\"20\" y=\"570\" width=\"350\" height=\"42\" fill=\"#161828\" rx=\"10\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#1E2035\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"36\" y=\"584\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">⟳</text><text x=\"54\" y=\"595\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#9EA3C0\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">What did we decide about Redis caching?</text><rect x=\"20\" y=\"620\" width=\"350\" height=\"42\" fill=\"#161828\" rx=\"10\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#1E2035\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"36\" y=\"634\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">⟳</text><text x=\"54\" y=\"645\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#9EA3C0\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Why are we migrating to Kubernetes?</text><rect x=\"20\" y=\"670\" width=\"350\" height=\"42\" fill=\"#161828\" rx=\"10\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#1E2035\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"36\" y=\"684\" font-size=\"12\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">⟳</text><text x=\"54\" y=\"695\" font-size=\"11\" fill=\"#9EA3C0\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"start\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Who owns the payments service?</text><rect x=\"20\" y=\"724\" width=\"350\" height=\"52\" fill=\"#161828\" rx=\"12\" opacity=\"1\" stroke=\"#1E2035\" stroke-width=\"1\"/><text x=\"68\" y=\"746\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"800\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">1.2K</text><text x=\"68\" y=\"762\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Total answers</text><text x=\"172\" y=\"746\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"800\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">87%</text><text x=\"172\" y=\"762\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Avg. confidence</text><text x=\"276\" y=\"746\" font-size=\"18\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"800\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">4.8</text><text x=\"276\" y=\"762\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Sources cited</text><rect x=\"0\" y=\"790\" width=\"390\" height=\"54\" fill=\"#0F1120\" rx=\"0\" opacity=\"1\"/><line x1=\"0\" y1=\"790\" x2=\"390\" y2=\"790\" stroke=\"#1E2035\" stroke-width=\"1\" opacity=\"1\"/><text x=\"48\" y=\"818\" font-size=\"20\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">⌂</text><text x=\"48\" y=\"834\" font-size=\"9\" fill=\"#818CF8\" font-weight=\"600\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-anchor=\"middle\" letter-spacing=\"0\" opacity=\"1\">Home</text><rect x=\"32\" y=\"792\" width=\"32\" height=\"2\" fill=\"#818CF8\" rx=\"1\" opacity=\"1\"/><text x=\"122\" y=\"818\" font-size=\"20\" fill=\"#5A5F7E\" font-weight=\"400\" font-family=\"Inter\" text-ancho